==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sideration
<hw>Sid`er*a"tion</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sideratio</ets>.]</ety> <def>The state of being siderated, or
planet-struck; esp., blast in plants; also, a sudden and apparently
causeless stroke of disease, as in apoplexy or paralysis.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Ray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sidereal</ent>⟦br⟧
